title: Xavier Woods And The New Day Subtly Joke About Woods’ Alleged Leaked Sex Tape With Paige On ‘Raw’
text:
During the weekend, WWE’s Paige was the victim of a leaked sex tap e which featured several WWE wrestlers including Xavier Woods of the New Day . 
After the tape made the rounds on the Internet there were, several rumors that Woods was going to be sidelined by the WWE due to his participation in the tape . 
Thankfully Woods did make an appearance on tonight’s Raw and subtly joked about the release of the sex tape during the New Day’s segment. 
New Day getting the Xavier Woods sex tape troll in tonight pic.twitter.com/AtDidQ8lpD 
— That Dude (@cjzer0) March 21, 2017 


New Day are the absolute best. For 3 seconds everyone in the world paused what they were doing. #RAW 
— WWE Creative Humor (@WWECreative_ish) March 21, 2017 
LOL that opening of The New Day segment was subtle but did exactly enough #RAW 
— Real Shoot Wrestling (@RSWLive) March 21, 2017 
Nice! They still kept New Day on TV. But the look Kofi and E gave Xavier Woods was priceless and genius!! #NewDay #Raw #XavierWoods 
— Maurice Jenkins (@INeed2GetLaid) March 21, 2017 


Big E: "Xavier, is there something you want to us about?"
Xavier: "WRESTLEMANIA!!"
That was perfect. Well done, #WWE /New Day. #Raw 
— Graham Matthews (@WrestleRant) March 21, 2017 
New Day in a backstage segment and Big E with a minor reference to the last few days' activities. #RAW 
— WrestlingINC.com (@WrestlingInc) March 21, 2017 

What a perfect way to address the entire controversy.
